reviews.text: Really tasty and inexpensive place to get traditional fish and chips
tried the pasta here, it's great. (except for the portion is not too generous)
Cozy little restaurant. I struggled to find it, but am also new to the area. The fish and chips will cure your craving at a reasonable price in Hong Kong. Service was normal, friendly staff.

Cozy little place with nice selection of burgers, pasta, milkshakes, coffee and tea. There was also a selection of fish & chips that I'll have to try next time. Prices are happily cheaper than average for Hong Kong. Finally, I highly recommend trying the Peanutbutter Milkshake - delicious!

Cozy place for weekend chitchat but may be a little bit noisy. Reasonably priced. No idea on the teabag with filter in pot 😛 but that’s fine

reviews.text: 好食😋
牛肉漢堡非常之好食，好Juicy 唔會有乾既感覺，雞肉漢堡都唔錯，唯獨是店舖周圍環境差左d，亦都唔算平，每樣野都要加錢，但想試好食既漢堡包就一定要黎試下。

可以做得更好的，不過，他們不願意。
看上去廚房至樓面都會年青人，有活力，也有衝勁；但就是不能持續。
吃的漢堡包味道確是好的，但就是不願意用心放好，仲使有竹簽也不能固定那包子。為甚麼？因為求其。
還有，本來是一所頗文青的小café，但昨晚兩男大聲談話，真的沒了興緻。
作為老闆，要持續維持餐廳質素，不單食物，更要維持品牌。
Overall 味道唔錯，卡邦尼意粉好味，辣肉腸意粉麻麻地，藍鱈魚意粉都唔錯，炸魚薯條唔錯，flat white 得喎，漢堡都好味，炸雞翼太油。
Really tasty and inexpensive place to get traditional fish and chips
